         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2455, recto: (1) Give it (2) to Peter (3) from Kyra.  You have (4) written to me about wheat.  (5) When the magistrate goes (6) away having loaded ---, I shall send (7) to you and you may send the camel, (8) and I shall load it with wheat for you.  -- (9) --.  Find means of coming (10) north.  ---.</ab>
